When my power runs thin"},{"s":64.98,"e":67.76,"text":"I can rise on my own"},{"s":67.76,"e":71.68,"text":"But I'd rather rise with him"},{"s":72.48,"e":74.74,"text":"Now I'm swinging from the curb"},{"s":75.32,"e":77.58,"text":"Like a kid in a sheet"},{"s":77.58,"e":80.86,"text":"Calling out my own name"},{"s":80.86,"e":83.16,"text":"In the dust of the street"},{"s":83.16,"e":86.2,"text":"And if I save one stranger"},{"s":86.2,"e":88.94,"text":"Then I'll save some part of me"},{"s":88.94,"e":91.86,"text":"Still I need that mercy"},{"s":91.86,"e":94.66,"text":"Like the river needs the sea"},{"s":94.66,"e":97.7,"text":"I know I'm only human"},{"s":98.24,"e":100.34,"text":"Trying on a flame"},{"s":100.34,"e":103.16,"text":"I can wear the mask, the cape"},{"s":103.16,"e":106.2,"text":"Still I whisper your name"},{"s":106.2,"e":107.5,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":109,"e":111.54,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":112.98,"e":116,"text":"With belief in my veins"},{"s":116,"e":117.4,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":117.48,"e":120.1,"text":"Jesus holds my rest"},{"s":120.1,"e":123.04,"text":"When my power runs thin"},{"s":123.04,"e":125.84,"text":"I can rise on my own"},{"s":125.84,"e":128.7,"text":"But I'd rather rise with him"},{"s":129.66,"e":133.5,"text":"So thank you, St. John's"},{"s":133.5,"e":135.74,"text":"For the bowls and the grates"},{"s":135.74,"e":138.82,"text":"For the men with tired eyes"},{"s":138.82,"e":141.4,"text":"And the names I can't replace"},{"s":141.4,"e":144.12,"text":"If I wasn't down so low"},{"s":144.12,"e":147,"text":"I might never understand"},{"s":147,"e":149.9,"text":"How a borrowed cup of soup"},{"s":149.9,"e":152.94,"text":"Can put strength in a man"},{"s":152.94,"e":154.26,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":155.76,"e":157.98,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":158.26,"e":162.68,"text":"With belief in my veins"},{"s":162.68,"e":164.12,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":164.22,"e":166.9,"text":"Jesus holds my best"},{"s":167.44,"e":169.74,"text":"When my power runs thin"},{"s":169.74,"e":172.56,"text":"I can rise on my own"},{"s":172.56,"e":175.66,"text":"But I'd rather rise with him"},{"s":177.84,"e":179.96,"text":"Thank you, St. John's"},{"s":179.96,"e":182.72,"text":"For the way you showed me"},{"s":182.72,"e":185.7,"text":"A crown can start as nothing"},{"s":188,"e":190.94,"text":"And still be holy"},{"s":193.44,"e":197.04,"text":"Oh, oh, oh"}],"duration":202.1199951171875,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:28:48.320Z","model":"whisper-1"}